---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Terms of Service" description="KlawAgent Terms of Service — the rules of the road.">

  <style>
    .hero-band {
      background: var(--bg-dark);
      color: var(--bg);
      padding: 72px 24px 64px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .hero-band .eyebrow { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.18em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
    .hero-band h1 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 3.5rem); font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.15; margin-bottom: 16px; }
    .hero-band .date { font-size: 0.875rem; color: #a09080; }

    .page-wrap { max-width: var(--max-w-text); margin: 0 auto; padding: 64px 24px 96px; }

    .summary-card { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent); border-radius: 12px; padding: 28px 32px; margin-bottom: 56px; }
    .summary-card .label { font-size: 0.7rem; letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 10px; }
    .summary-card p { font-size: 1.05rem; font-style: italic; }

    section { margin-bottom: 52px; }
    section h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 20px; padding-bottom: 12px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
    section h3 { font-size: 0.875rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--text-muted); margin: 24px 0 10px; }
    section p { margin-bottom: 12px; }

    ul.check-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; }
    ul.check-list li { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 10px; font-size: 0.9375rem; }
    ul.check-list li::before { content: "✓"; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 700; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; }

    ul.block-list { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 12px; }
    ul.block-list li { background: var(--bg-card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px; padding: 14px 18px; font-size: 0.9375rem; }

    .warning-card { background: #fff8f0; border: 1px solid #f0d9c0; border-left: 4px solid #d97706; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px 28px; margin-top: 16px; }
    .warning-card p { font-size: 0.9375rem; color: #7c4a00; margin: 0; }

    .contact-card { background: var(--bg-dark); color: var(--bg); border-radius: 16px; padding: 36px 32px; text-align: center; margin-top: 56px; }
    .contact-card h2 { font-family: var(--font-serif); font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; border: none; padding: 0; color: var(--bg); }
    .contact-card p { color: #a09080; margin-bottom: 24px; font-size: 0.9375rem; }
    .contact-card a { display: inline-block; background: var(--accent); color: #fff; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 999px; padding: 12px 28px; font-size: 0.75rem; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.1em; text-transform: uppercase; transition: background 0.2s; }
    .contact-card a:hover { background: var(--accent-hover); }
  </style>

  <div class="hero-band">
    <p class="eyebrow">Legal</p>
    <h1>Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="date">Last updated: February 19, 2026</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-wrap">

    <div class="summary-card">
      <p class="label">The Short Version</p>
      <p>Use KlawAgent responsibly. The service is provided as-is. You're responsible for how your AI agent is configured and what it does on your behalf.</p>
    </div>

    <section>
      <h2>Using KlawAgent</h2>
      <h3>The Service</h3>
      <p>KlawAgent is a managed AI agent platform. We deploy, host, and maintain your AI agent so you can focus on your business. By using KlawAgent, you agree to these terms.</p>
