        <li>Data loss or security issues arising from third-party services</li>
        <li>Downtime or service interruptions</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Paid Services</h2>
      <ul class="check-list">
        <li>All prices are in USD unless otherwise stated</li>
        <li>Refunds are available within 30 days, no questions asked</li>
        <li>Your subscription is for your business use only and is non-transferable</li>
        <li>We reserve the right to update pricing with reasonable notice</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2>Changes to These Terms</h2>
      <p>We may update these terms occasionally. Continued use of the service after changes constitutes acceptance. Significant changes will be announced on the website and via email.</p>
    </section>

    <div class="contact-card">
      <h2>Questions About These Terms?</h2>
      <p>We're happy to clarify anything. Just reach out.</p>
      <a href="mailto:hey@klawagent.ai">hey@klawagent.ai</a>
